quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  70,11,"Kala ma…ì…ìe yi'ay …ìadondiraa…óo mun on ka suu…óaaki. Wondude e …óum fof gooto lamndotaako fii oya hakkee ko annde. Hanndu…óo e Yiite ngen yeloo jonnugol …ìi…ó…ìe makko …ìen fii sottorgol mo lette …óen."
  70,12,"O sottora gennda makko e neene gooto makko on."
  70,13,"o sottora kadi gorol makko …ìa…óii…ìe mo, …ìen …ìannitaynoo …ìe mo si sattii."
  70,14,"O sottora kadi kala yim…ìe e jinna ekw ko woni kon ka leydi, refti o jonnira …óum fii sottoragol, da…ónda hoore makko lette Yiite ngen."
  70,15,"∆äum gasirtaa wano bon…óo on yelori. Yiite laakara ngen ko uuyaynge hu…ì…ìa."
  70,16,"∆Åoltaynge wippita guri hoore; hakkee ko nge wuli e konge hu…ì…ìi."
  70,17,"Hinge nodda on …óuurnii…óo goonga, o hucciti o salii gom…óinnde mbo o ronki gollude."
  70,18,"O moo…ìi jawle, o mari ndi fii wata o nafqu ndi e laawol Allah."
  70,19,"Pellet, ne…ó…óo on tagaama ko o tii…óu…óo reer…óugol."
  70,20,"Si lorra nawnaare maa baasal memii mo, tawaa ko o fan…óu…óo mu√±al."
  70,21,"Si ko he…ìii mbo ko weltinta hono amo e ngalu he…ìii mo, o wona tii…óu…óo salorgol …óum e fii laawol Allah ngol."
  70,22,"Si wanaa juuloo…ìe …ìen, …ìen …óon hino hisi e …óin jikkuuji ≈ãi√±aa…ói."
  70,23,"∆Åen taw…ìe ko duumii…ìe e juulde ma…ì…ìe nden, …ìe welsindotaako e mayre, …ìe tottira nde e waqtu mayre happaa…óo on."
  70,24,"E …ìen taw…ìe hino e jawle ma…ì…ìe …óen ge…ìal dottangal farlangal."
  70,25,"Ge…ìal nagl …ìe ittanta torotoo…óo …ìe e baaso mo torortaako."
  70,26,"E …ìen goooginany…ìe √ëalaande Darngal nden. √ëalnde Allah yo…ìitoyta kala e ko o haanndi kon."
  70,27,"E …ìen taw…ìe hi…ìe huli lette Joomi ma…ì…ìe …óen, e hoore ko …ìe ardini e golle mo∆¥∆¥e kon fow."
  70,28,"Pellet, lette Joomi ma…ì…ìe …óen, ko hul…ìinii…óe …óe haqqil…óo haanaa hoolaade da…óugol."
  70,29,"E …ìen taw…ìe hino reenir…ìe farjuuji ma…ì…ìe …óin : surragol wo…ó…óitoo e pankare."
  70,30,"Si wanaa e rew…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen maa e hor…ìe ko …ìe jeyi kon, …ìe feletaake …óon on fii dakmitorgol …ìen mbalndi e tanaa mun."
  70,31,"Kala non …óa…ì…ìu…óo ka dakmitora hara wanaa e …ìen rew…ìe e hor…ìe jantaa…ìe, haray ko …ìen woi yawtu…ìe keeri Allah …óin."
  70,32,"E …ìen taw…ìe si …ìe hoolnaama e jawle e gunndoo ekw, e aynitoo…ìe ahadiiji ma…ì…ìe …óin e yim…ìe …ìen kulol wata hoolaare bonu …ìe firtatah aadi."
  70,33,"E …ìen taw…ìe ko √±ii…ìir…ìe e seedeeji ma…ì…ìe …óin no haaniri, tawata jeydal maa e ngayngu battintaa e mun."
  70,34,"E …ìen taw…ìe hi…ìe reenorii e julde ma…ì…ìe nden, tottirgol nden e waqtu mayre, wonndude e laa…ìal e dee∆¥ere, hara huunde sokoli≈ãtaa …ìe e mayre."
  70,35,"∆Åen siforaa…ìe …óin sifaaji, …ìe teddiniroyte e Aljannaaji, neemaaji √±ii…ìu…ói, e ndaaroygol Yeeso Allah Teddungo ngon."
  70,36,"E ko nanngi sirkoo…ìe jeyaa…ìe e yim…ìe maa …ìen, an Nulaa…óo, hi…ìe he√±ora fennugol ma?"
  70,37,"Hi…ìe huu…ìitir-maa ka √±aamo e ka nano, ko…ìe dentoy-dentoy."
  70,38,"Hara gooto kala e ma…ì…ìe tam∆¥ini nde Allah naadoyta mo Aljanna neemaaji, ka o neeminorta neemaaji duumii…ói, e hoore ko o heddii e keeferaaku mum?"
  70,39,"Wanaa no …ìe sikkiri non ! Men tagiri…ìe e ko …ìe anndi fii mun, woni ndihal hoykal, …ìe lohiri non kam…ìe kadi, tawde …ìe waawah nafude ko'e ma…ì…ìe wanah fii lorra. Ko honno non …ìe townitorta?"